      • assertErrors

        public void assertErrors(java.lang.String title,
                java.lang.String upIdName,
                java.lang.String eleType,
                java.lang.String fileName,
                long timeout)
        get and write browser message to file using autoit compiled exe. you can use it like this: assertErrors(title, "errorMessage", "li", "D:\\a.txt", 10);
        参数:
        title - pop window title
        upIdName - the id or name of the text's father element
        eleType - the type of the element which to get text
        fileName - file path and name to store the error text
        timeout - time out setting to find the pop window
        抛出:
        java.lang.RuntimeException
